.TH "omsemogo-by-bamboosh-win32" "6" "2016-01-17" "omse mogo User Manuals" ""
.hy
.SH NAME
.PP
omsemogo-by-bamboosh-win32 - launcher for omse mogo
.SH SYNOPSIS
.PP
omsemogo-by-bamboosh-win32 [\f[I]options\f[R]]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
omsemogo-by-bamboosh-win32 - is the launcher for omse mogo that call
PlayOnLinux in backend.
demo ranked 2nd at The Gathering 2000
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
--help
Display help for the command
.TP
--setdesktop
Set to desktop mode and run (can go in fullscreen)
.TP
--version
Display version and author information
.SH ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
.TP
\ APP_RES [widthxheight]
start the app in a widthxheight virtual desktop
.PD 0
.P
.PD
ex.
APP_RES=800x600 omsemogo-by-bamboosh-win32
